query: select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, '=7' + substring(Don.Barcode, 4, 4) Ent from PersonCards PerC join Donations Don on PerC.UniqueId = Don.DonorId
select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, substring(Don.Barcode, 6, 6) Ent from PersonCards PerC join Donations Don on PerC.UniqueId = Don.DonorId
select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, substring(Don.Barcode, 3, 9) Ent from PersonCards PerC join Donations Don on PerC.UniqueId = Don.DonorId
select top (1) PerC.UniqueId, Don.Barcode Ent from PersonCards PerC join Donations Don on PerC.UniqueId = Don.DonorId
